    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>Look at its length:</p>\n\n<pre><code>int[] i = ...;\nif (i.length == 0) { } // no elements in the array\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Though it's safer to check for null at the same time:</p>\n\n<pre><code>if (i == null || i.length == 0) { }\n</code></pre>\n"
