    "body" : "<p>I believe that what you want is</p>\n\n<pre><code>int[] k = new int[3];\n\nif (k != null) {  // Note, != and not == as above\n    System.out.println(k.length);\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>You newed it up so it was never going to be null.</p>\n"
